 a conversion machine.​ Our team of experts will evaluate your site and identify specific areas for conversion improvements. https://bit.ly/3lcgILt','https://bit.ly/3lcgILt',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0),(10,4,'2020-09-21 17:18:39','New resource updates to the Open Source page on Magento.com. ','Check out the updated Open Source page on Magento.com. Learn how to maximize your Open Source store, discover offers for Open Source merchants, and view comparison charts between Open Source and Magento Commerce. Go to page: https://adobe.ly/3kCB5jW','https://adobe.ly/3kCB5jW',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0),(11,4,'2020-09-25 01:48:09','Don&#039;t miss Adobe Developer&#039;s Live: Commerce which brings together developers and experience builders in a one-day free conference on Monday, Sept 28th. ','The one-day free conference will feature important Magento developer updates, technical sessions and community networking opportunities. Adobe product teams across Adobe Experience Cloud will showcase the latest tech advances and developer tools powering customer experience management across industries. Register now: https://bit.ly/3hYzbrX','https://bit.ly/3hYzbrX',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0),(12,4,'2020-09-28 00:00:00','BUY MORE - SAVE MORE - PAY LESS','10% to 25% discount on every extension depending on how much you buy. Check it out. Don&#039;t miss out','https://www.mageplaza.com/deals/?utm_source=notification&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=sale-12',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0),(13,4,'2020-09-28 22:07:26','Is Your Website Selling as Much as It Can? Watch our on-demand webinar and learn how to turn your website into a conversion machine.','Watch our on-demand webinar: Is Your Website Selling As Much As It Can? Digital Strategist Ereika Stimley and eCommerce Consultant Corey Gelato will walk you through a website self-assessment and live demo that will help you uncover opportunities to increase conversions and grow revenues. Watch now: https://bit.ly/2EAujMc','https://bit.ly/2EAujMc',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0),(14,4,'2020-10-06 16:53:57','[Commerce Webinar] Is Your Website Ready for the 2020 Holiday Season?','Join us for a fireside chat on October 15th to learn how to prepare for the increase in web traffic during the holiday months. Anthony Potgieter, Senior Manager of E-Commerce for Wyze, and Slava Kravchuk, Founder and CEO of Atwix will discuss their top tips for succeeding this holiday season. Register today: https://bit.ly/33wzXbC','https://bit.ly/33wzXbC',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0),(15,4,'2020-10-06 16:53:57','[Webinar] Is your site to ready to handle spikes in traffic and transactions? ','Your site speed can make or break your conversion rate this holiday season and beyond. Join us on October 15th for a fireside chat &quot;Is Your Website Ready for the 2020 Holiday Season?&quot; to learn what Commerce features you must have, and how to scale your webstore to maximize conversion rates. If you can&#039;t make the live webinar, be sure to register anyway and we&#039;ll send you the recording and slides afterward. Register today: https://bit.ly/33wzXbC','https://bit.ly/33wzXbC',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0),(16,4,'2020-10-13 14:23:08','[Last Chance To Register] Is your website ready for major growth?','Explosive growth can happen any time. Is your website ready? Join us on October 15th for a fireside chat to learn how to scale your webstore and prepare for spikes in web traffic during the holidays and beyond. If you can&#039;t make the live webinar, register anyway and we&#039;ll sending the recording afterward. Register now: https://bit.ly/33wzXbC','https://bit.ly/33wzXbC',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0),(17,4,'2020-10-15 07:18:11','MultiSafepay install','MultiSafepay: Check out our documentation page to setup your webshop','https://docs.multisafepay.com/integrations/magento2/manual/',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0),(18,4,'2020-10-15 07:18:11','MultiSafepay upgrade','MultiSafepay: Check out our documentation p